This issue is a result of a support issue https://support.atlassian.com/browse/JSP-72642

Currently, text with markup (wiki or other) in the description field is rendered as simple text in the Activity fields (particularly the history field). This becomes unreadable, especially in cases where there are small changes to a large text in the description field. Also, for those using the TinyMCE plugin renderer, this becomes quite critical.

Apparently, the problem is due to the inability to configure a renderer for the activity history field. Proposal is to enable such configuration.

