There is one step backwards in the issue navigator in comparison to version 3.x: If you change a stored filter you will get the info *"Filter modified since loading"* but no further hint anymore how to get the filter operations for instance to save the modified filter. Especially new JIRA users really often ask me how to save a modified filter when he is in the simple searching mode. And I really understand there query! How to know that the user has to change into the summary tab or into the advanced searching mode to do so.

It would be perfect (and I guess it would be very easy) also to put the filter operation sections to the "simple" searching mode (as it exists in the summary tab and in the advanced searching mode).

