JIRA throw System Error 'Property Not Found' error when try to fix the error as suggested by the Integrity Checker. This is happening in JIRA 3.13.4 with inconsistent data.

Generally, the bug is reproduce-able with inconsistent data as follow:
# Run Integrity Checker
# Integrity Checker throw 
{quote}
Check that all SearchRequest Portlets are associated with a valid SearchRequest
   ERROR:	 User admin has a Portlet for SearchRequest with id '13811'
{quote}
# Try to fix the error by hitting on the "Fix" button and Integrity Checker return throw stack trace:
{noformat}
com.opensymphony.module.propertyset.PropertyImplementationException: Property not found
{noformat}

